SwissLipids API advanced search function

Source: R/search.R
swissLipidsAdvancedSearch.Rd

`swissLipidsAdvancedSearch` Performs an advanced search using the SwissLipids API

swissLipidsAdvancedSearch(
  name = NA_character_,
  smiles = NA_character_,
  inchikey = NA_character_,
  formula = NA_character_,
  mz = NA_real_,
  adduct = NA_character_,
  massErrorRate = NA_real_
)

Arguments

name

`character`
smiles

`character`
inchikey

`character`
formula

`character`
mz

`numeric`
adduct

`character`
massErrorRate

`numeric`

Value

`data.frame` A named list with the search results

Examples
